### Register a Customer
POST http://localhost:5220/customers/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "johndoe@example.com",
  "address": "123 Main Street"
}


### Update a Customer
PUT http://localhost:5220/customers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "janedoe@example.com",
  "address": "456 Elm Street"
}


### Retrieve Customer Details
GET http://localhost:5220/customers/1


### Delete a Customer
DELETE http://localhost:5220/customers/1


### Register a Customer with Null Values
POST http://localhost:5220/customers/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "invalidemail",
  "address": ""
}